tafsir[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"GomЙ—ii malaama gomЙ—inЙ“e Alla gollirooЙ“e sari'a Makko Й“en sabu hiЙ“ugol maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“aynoo kon, e daЙ—ugol ko Й“e hulunoo kon."
  23,2,"ЖҒen koЙ“e e nder Julde maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e hoykiniiЙ“e, hara terde maЙ“Й“e Й—en no deeЖҙi e nder mayre, Й“erЙ—e maЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en no yeewi immorde e soklaaji."
  23,3,"E Й“en Й—urniiЙ“e e meere nden e puyndan Й—an e kala ko goopi immorde e konguЙ—i Й—in maaЙ—um kuuЙ—e Й—en."
  23,4,"E Й“en gollayЙ“e fii laЙ“Й“inngol wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in immorde jikkuuji bonЙ—i, e laЙ“Й“inirgol jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en yaltinngol Jakka majje."
  23,5,"E Й“en Й“e kaГұun ko reenirЙ“e farjuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in woЙ—Й—intingol Й—i e jeeno(jina) e luutiyaagu e bonkiiji Й—in, kamЙ“e ko Й“e nefooЙ“e ko boni laaЙ“uЙ“e."
  23,6,"Si wanaa e sonnaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e maaЙ—um ko Й“e mari kon immorde e horЙ“e, haray kamЙ“e Й“e feletaake fii dakmitorgolЙ“e mbalndi e tanaa mu'un."
  23,7,"Kala Й—aЙ“Й“uЙ—o dakmitorgol ko wonaa sonnaaЙ“e makko Й“en maaЙ—um horЙ“e makko Й“e o jeyi Й“en, haray kanko ko o yawtuЙ—o keeri Alla Й—in sabu yawtugol ko O dagini kon dakmitorgol yaha e ko O harmini kon e mu'un."
  23,8,"E Й“en Й“e kaГұun koЙ“e reenuЙ“e ko Alla halfini Й“e kon, maaЙ—um ko jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en halfini Й“e kon, e aadiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“e yeebataako Й—i, ko woni hiЙ“e humna Й—i."
  23,9,"E Й“en Й“e kaГұun koЙ“e reenirЙ“e JulЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en duumagol e majje, e tottugol Й—e e nder waqtuuji majje e wonndude e ruknuuji majje e waЙ—Й—iiЙ—i majje e yiЙ—aaЙ—i majje."
  23,10,"ЖҒee siforЙ“e Й—ii sifaaji Й—oo ko kamЙ“e woni ronooЙ“e Й“en."
  23,11,"ЖҒen Й“e no ronoya Aljanna Й“urЙ—o toowude on kamЙ“e ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ayЙ“e e nder makko poomaa, neemaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in taЖҙataa nder ton."
  23,12,"GomЙ—ii Men tagii baaba Й“anndinke on Aadama immorde e loopal, Жҙettaama mbullaare mu'un immorde e tamannde yaltinaande e ndiyam jillondirЙ—am e mbullaari leydi ndin."
  23,13,"Refti Men tagi geЙ—alЙ“e(genyol) makko Й“en ko Й“e jibinayЙ“e immorde e toЙ“Й“ere [maniiyu] nde no ГұiiЙ“a ka rennga haa fewndo jibinngol ngol."
  23,14,"Men Tagi Й“aawo Й—um toЙ“Й“ere ГұiiЙ“unde nden ka rannga heЙ—Й—ere woЙ—eere, refti Men waЙ—i nden toЙ“Й“ere woЙ—eere wano huyre teewu Жҙakkande, Men Tagi huyre nden Жҙi'e saЙ—tuЙ—e, Men Й“orni Й—en Жҙi'e teewu, refti Men fuЙ—Й—i mo Tagu goo sabu wuttugol ruuhu on e makko, e yaltinngol mo faade e ngurndan, Barkii Alla MoЖҙЖҙo TaguЙ—o."
  23,15,"Refti onon yimЙ“e Й“en, Й“aawo kon ko wuliЙ—on wuliЙ—on(bennudon) e mu'un immorde e Й—in Й“orЙ—i(jolde) aray maayon tuma huuЙ“ugol laje mooЙ—on."
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon Й“aawo maayugol mooЙ—on ko on imminoyteeЙ“e ka genaale mo'on Г‘alnde Darngal; fii yo on hasbe e dow kon ko ardinnoЙ—on immorde e golle."
  23,17,"GomЙ—ii Men Tagii dow mooЙ—on -onon yimЙ“e Й“en- kammuuli jeeЙ—iЙ—i yoga e majji no dow yoga, Men laataaki welsindiiЙ“e fii tagu Amen ngun, Men wonaali kadi yejjituЙ“e ngu."
  23,18,"Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam tuЙ“o ngon emmbere haaju on, wanaa Й—uuЙ—uЙ—am sakko Й—am bonna wanaa kadi fanЙ—uЙ—am sakko Й—am lella, Men waЙ—i Й—am ГұiiЙ“ayЙ—am ka leydi, yimЙ“e Й“en e daabeeji Й—in no nafitora Й—am, pellet, Menen ko Men HattanЙ“e e dow naЙ“ugol Й—am hara on nafitoraaki [Й—am]."
  23,19,"Men fuЙ—Й—ani on sabu Й—amnd iyam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on e majje dimЙ—e limiiЙ—e mbaadiiji e nooneeji, wano Жҙibbeeje e rummaanaaje e poomuuje, ko e majje Гұaamoton."
  23,20,"Men fuЙ—Й—ani on sabu majjan leЙ—Й—e nebbannje Й—en Й—e no yalta ka fello Siinaa, hiЙ—e fuЙ—ina nebban yaltiteeЙ—an Й—an immorde e dimЙ—e majje hiЙ—an wujee hiЙ—an maafiree kadi."
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on -onon yimЙ“e Й“en- e neemoraaЙ—i Й—in (gelooЙ—i Й—in, na'i Й—in, dammi Й—in) tasakuyee e dallinorЙ—um ko hiЙ—on tinndinora e dow kattanЙ—e Alla e Newanagol Mo on, MeЙ—en yarna on goЙ—Й—um e ko woni kon e nder deedi Й—ii neemoraaЙ—i kosam laaЙ“uЙ—am lewГұuЙ—am wonande yarooЙ“e Й“en, no woodani on kadi e majji nafooje heewuЙ—e Й—e hiЙ—on naftora Й—um e majji; wano waЙ—Й—agol ngol e teefi Й—in e leeЙ“i Й—in, hiЙ—on Гұaama kadi immorde e tebbuuli majji."
  23,22,"Ko e hoore gelooЙ—i Й—in immorde neemoraaЙ—i Й—in ka njorndi, e hoore laaЙ—e Й—en ka maayo roonndeteЙ—on."
  23,23,"GomЙ—ii Men Nuliino Nuuhu (yo o his) ka yimЙ“e makko Й“en himo noddaЙ“e faade e Alla, o wi'ani Й“e: ""Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, Rewee Alla Kanko tun, alanaa on reweteeЙ—o e Goonga tanaa Makko O Senike. Kaa on hulirtaa Alla Й—oftagol YamiraaЙ—i Makko Й—in e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in?!"""
  23,24,"KoohooЙ“e tedduЙ“e Й“en e yedduЙ“e Alla Й“en e yimЙ“e makko Й“en Й“e wi'ani jokkuЙ“e Й“e Й“en e puyЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en: ""Oo wonЙ—o nodditaade wonnde kanko ko o NulaaЙ—o o wonaali si wanaa ko o Й“anndinke wano mo'on, ko o faalaa ko heynaade e hoonaade e hoore mo'on. Sinndo Alla muuyuno nulugol e meeЙ—en NulaaЙ—o O Nulayno mo hara ko o jeyaaЙ—o e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en, O nulataa mo hara ko e yimЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa, Men nanaali sifa koo ko o nodditii Й—oo ka maamiraaЙ“e amen adiiЙ“e men Й“en""."
  23,25,"Kanko o wonaali si wanaa gorko mo feetere woni e mu'un, o anndaa ko o woni e wowlude, habbee mo haa fiyaake makko on Й“anngana yimЙ“e Й“en."
  23,26,"Nuuhu (yo o his) maaki: ""Joom am, wallam e hoore maЙ“Й“e Й—um woni yoЙ“tanoЙ—aa lam e maЙ“Й“e sabu ko Й“e finni lam kon""."
  23,27,"Men wahayini e makko; Й—um woni moЖҙЖҙin laana kan e ndenka Amen e no Men anndinmaa hono no moЖҙЖҙinirtaa ka, si yamiroore Amen nden arii fii halkugol Й“e, ndiyam Й—am pullitori doole e nokkuure nden ka bireedi(mburu) juЙ—etee Й—on, naadu e nder makka immorde e kala ko wuuri gorun e deyun fii yo geyngol ngol jokkondir, naadu Й“eynguure maaЙ—a nden si wanaa Й“en Й“e Daalol Alla ngol aditii fii halkeede; wano sonnaajo maaЙ—a on e Й“iЙ—Й—o maaЙ—a on, wata a noddam fii yo Mi danndu Й“en tooГұirЙ“e geddi halkeede, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e halkirteeЙ“e -feere alaa- yoolagol ka waame ndiyam."
  23,28,"Si a Жҙawii ka laana an e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e maaЙ—a immorde e gomЙ—inЙ“e daЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, haray maaku: ""Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, On dannduЙ—o en immorde e yimЙ“e heefereeЙ“e Й“en O halki Й“e."
  23,29,"Maaku: ""Joom am, jippinam ka leydi jippinngol barkinaangol, ko An woni MoЖҙЖҙo jippinoowo""."
  23,30,"Pellet, no e nder Й—um ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo immorde e danndugol Nuuhu e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en wonndude e makko, e halkeede yedduЙ“e Й“en; daliilaaji feeГұuЙ—i e dow kattanЙ—e Amen fii wallugol NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en e halkungol fennuЙ“e Й“e Й“en, fii kala Men wonii ko Men jarriborЙ“e yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en Nulugol mo faade e maЙ“Й“e fii yo Й“anngu hakkunde gomЙ—inЙ—o on e keefeero on maaЙ—um Й—oftiiЙ—o on e geddo on."
  23,31,"Refti Men fuЙ—Й—i Й“aawo halkeede yimЙ“e Nuuhu Й“en mofte goo."
  23,32,"Men Nuli e maЙ“Й“e NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e himo noddaЙ“e ka Alla, o maakani Й“e: ""Rewee Alla Kanko tun alanaa on reweteeЙ—o e Goonga tanaa Makko O Senike. Enee, kaa on hulirtaa Alla woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in e jokkugol YamiraaЙ—i Makko Й—in?!"""
  23,33,"KoohooЙ“e tedduЙ“e Й“en ka yimЙ“e makko yedduЙ“e Alla, Й“e fenni Laakara on e ko woni ton kon immorde mbarjaari e Lepte, ko Men yaajinani Й“e kon immorde e neemaaji ka ngurdan aduna bewini Й“e. ЖҒe wi'ani jokkuЙ“e Й“e Й“en e puyЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en- : ""Oo wonaali si wanaa Й“anndunke yeru mooЙ—on himo Гұaama ko Гұaamoton kon, himo yara ko yaroton kon, o maraa ko senndi mo e mooЙ—on haa tawa o imminee NulaaЙ—o faade e mooЙ—on""."
  23,34,"Mi woondii si on Й—oftike Й“anndinke wano mo'on, pellet, ontuma haray onon ko on hayruЙ“e sabu waasude nafitorgol mo'on Й—oftagol mo sabu Й—alugol mooЙ—on sanamuuji mon Й—in, e jokkugol on mo Й“ural alanaa Й—um e dow mooЙ—on."
  23,35,"Enee, oo aaЖҙiiЙ—o wonnde ko o NulaaЙ—o, o fodu on wonnde si on maayii on wontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e kiЙ—Й—e wonndema onon on yaltinoyte ka genaale mooЙ—on hara ko on wuuruЙ“e?! mbela Й—um ko hakkille ?!"
  23,36,"No woЙ—Й—i haa fanti kon ko fodaЙ—on Й—um immorde e yaltinegol ka genaali mooЙ—on hara ko on wuuruЙ“e Й“aawo mayde mooЙ—on, e wontugol mooЙ—on mbullaari e Жҙi'e kiЙ—Й—e."
  23,37,"Ngurdam Й—am wonaali si wanaa ngurdam aduna Й—am, wanah ngurdam Laakara, wuuruЙ“e Й“en e amen no maay hara Й“e wuuritataa, woЙ“Й“e goo kadi jibinee Й“e wuura, men wonaali yaltinoyteeЙ“e Й“aawo mayde amen nden fii hasboore Г‘alnde darngal."
  23,38,"Oo wonЙ—o nodditaade wonndema ko o NulaaЙ—o faade e mooЙ—on o wonaali si wonaa gorko fefindii-Й—o fawi e Alla sabu ngol nodditagol makko, men wonaali gomЙ—inooЙ“e mo."
  23,39,"NulaaЙ—o on maaki: ""Joomam, wallam e hoore maЙ“Й“e Й—um woni yoЙ“tanoЙ—aa lam e maЙ“Й“e sabu ko Й“e finni lam kon""."
  23,40,"Alla jaabori mo Daalugol: ""ЖҒaawo jamaanu fanЙ—uЙ—o aray Й“ee fennuЙ“e ko adduЙ—aa kon wonta nimsuЙ“e e dow ko Й“e wonnoo fennude kon""."
  23,41,"Hito saЙ—tungo halkayngo nanngi Й“e sabu hanndu- gol maЙ“Й“e e Lepte Й—en e sanndalЙ—aagu maЙ“Й“e, Й—e wattini Й“e halkiiЙ“e yeru duuГұo ilol ngol, halakuyee wonanii yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en."
  23,42,"Refti Й“aawo halkeede maЙ“Й“e Men fuЙ—Й—i yimЙ“e e moftaaji goo wano yimЙ“e Luutu, e yimЙ“e Su'aybu, e yimЙ“e Yuunusa."
  23,43,"Adintinantaake mofte woo mofte e Й—ii moftaaji fennuЙ—i, waqtu happaaЙ—o on fii arugol halakuyee majje on, Й—e nennataake kadi gaayi happu ngun, noone woo no laatorani Й—e immorde e laawi Й—in."
  23,44,"Refti Men Nuli NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en ko Й“e jokkondi-Й“e NulaaЙ—o feЖҙЖҙa NulaaЙ—o goo lontoo, tuma kala ari e mofte immorde e Й—in moftaaji NulaaЙ—o majje on Й“e fenna mo, Men jokkiniri yoga e maЙ“Й“e yoga halkeede, woodeede heddanaaki Й“e si wanaa yeru ko yimЙ“e Й“en haalata kon fii maЙ“Й“e, halkaare woodanii yimЙ“e Й“e gomЙ—inaali ko NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en addani Й“e kon immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  23,45,"Refti Men Nuli Muusaa e musiЙ—Й—o makko on Haaruuna wonndude e Aayeeje Amen Й—en jeenay: (Tuggordu ndun, Junngo ngon, Kanuuji Й—in, tenЙ—i Й—in, ЖіiiЖҙam Й—am, Waameere nden, Kokke Й—en, Uytagol dimЙ—e Й—en), e hujja Й“annguЙ—o."
  23,46,"Men Nuli Й“e faade e Fir'awna e teddinaaЙ“e Й“en ka yimЙ“e makko Й“e mawninkinii, Й“e Й—owtaaki gomЙ—n- gol [Muusaa e Haaruuna], Й“e woni yimЙ“e townitor- Й“e e hoore yimЙ“e Й“en doolugol e tooГұugol."
  23,47,"ЖҒe wi'i: ""E hara men gomЙ—inay Й“anndinkeeЙ“e Й—iЙ—o yeruuЙ“e amen, alaa ko Й“e senndondiri e amen, e kadi yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en (Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en) ko Й—oftiiЙ“e amen yankinaniiЙ“e [amen]?"""
  23,48,"ЖҒe fenni Й“en Й—iЙ—o e ko Й“e addi kon immorde ka Alla, sabu fennugol maЙ“Й“e ngol Й“e woni halkiraaЙ“e yoolagol."
  23,49,"GomЙ—ii Men Okkiino Muusaa Tawreetaare nden jortagol wonnde yimЙ“e makko Й“en feeweray nde faade e Goonga kan, Й“e gollitira nde."
  23,50,"Men waЙ—i Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Mariyama on e yumma mak- ko Mariyama Maande tinndinnde e KattaЙ—e Amen Й—en, gomЙ—ii Men waЙ—ii mo sowiiЙ—o ko aldah e baa- biraawo, Men werni Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o fe nokkuure towtunde ka leydi, fotondirnde moЖҙЖҙunde fii ГұiiЙ“ugol e mayre, no e mayre ndiyam iloojam heyЙ—itay Й—am."
  23,51,"Ko onon yo NulaaЙ“e, Гұaamee laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Mi daginani on Гұaamugol Й—in, gollon golle moЖҙЖҙe hawrondirЙ—e e Sari'a, pellet Min, ko Mi AnnduЙ—o ko golloton kon immorde e golle, suuЙ—anaaki lam immorde e golle mo'on Й—en hay e huunde."
  23,52,"E pellet, Diina mooЙ—on kan -onon NulaaЙ“e Й“en- ko Diina woota, kan le ko Lislaamu, ko Min woni jom mo'on, on maraa Jooma tanaa Am, huliree Lam Й—oftagol yimiraaЙ—i Am Й—in, e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Am Й—in."
  23,53,"JokkuЙ“e Й“e Й“en sennditii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e ka Diina, Й“e wonti feddeeji e dente, fedde kala no weltori ko nde gomЙ—ini kon wonndema ko Й—um woni diina weltoraaka kan ka Alla, hara nde yeЖҙЖҙitotaako faade e ko woni kon ka wonnde goo."
  23,54,"Terto Й“e-an NulaaЙ—o- e ko Й“e woni kon e muuЙ—um immorde e majjere e wemmbere nden haa tuma jippagol Lepte Й—en e maЙ“Й“e."
  23,55,"Kaa hara Й—ii feddeeji wasorayЙ—i ko woni kon ka majji sikku wonndema ko Men okki Й“e kon immore e jawle Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“en ka ngurnda aduna Й—um ko yaccinanngol Й“e moЖҙЖҙere nde Й“e hanndi e mu'un?! Fiyaake on wonah no Й“e sikkirta non, anndu MeЙ—en okka Й“e Й—um fuuntirgol e Й—aynugol Й“e, kono kamЙ“e Й“e alaa so'ude Й—um."
  23,56,"Kaa hara Й—ii feddeeji wasorayЙ—i ko woni kon ka majji sikku wonndema ko Men okki Й“e kon immore e jawle Й—en e Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“en ka ngurnda aduna Й—um ko yaccinanngol Й“e moЖҙЖҙere nde Й“e hanndi e mu'un?! Fiyaake on wonah no Й“e sikkirta non, anndu MeЙ—en okka Й“e Й—um hebbinorЙ—um e Й—aynugol Й“e, kono kamЙ“e Й“e alah so'ude Й—um."
  23,57,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e kaГұum wonndude e gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e ngal e moЖҙЖҙugol maЙ“Й“e ngol ko Й“e huluЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  23,58,"E Й“en Й“e kaГұum ko Й“e gomЙ—inЙ“e Aayeeje Deftere Makko nden."
  23,59,"E Й“en Й“e kaГұum ko Й“e wootinЙ—inЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e sirkantah Mo hay e huunde."
  23,60,"E Й“en Й“e no tinnoo e golle dewal ngal, Й“e Й“attora ka Alla golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en hara hiЙ“e huli fii wata Alla ronku jaЙ“annde Й“e nafkugol maЙ“Й“e ngol e golle maЙ“Й“e moЖҙЖҙe Й—en si Й“e ruttoyike ka Makko Г‘alnde Darngal."
  23,61,"ЖҒen sifaaЙ“e Й—ii sifaaji mawЙ—i, hiЙ“e heГұoo faade e golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e adondirayЙ“e e majje, ko sabu Й—um Й“e adori tanaa maЙ“Й“e."
  23,62,"Men fawaali wonkii woo si wanaa emmbere ko ki hattanaa kon gollugol, Deftere no ka Amen Men tabintinii e nder mayre gollal kala golluЙ—o, hinde wowla Goonga, kan ka sikke woo alah e nder mu'un, hara kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұiroytaake uytaneede moЖҙЖҙi maЙ“Й“e Й—in, wanaa fii non Й“eydaneede bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in."
  23,63,"Ko woni, Й“erЙ—e heeferЙ“e Й“en no e nder welsindaa- re immorde ndee Deftere, nden wowlaynde Goo- nga kan, e Deftere jippiinde nden e maЙ“Й“e, no woodani Й“e kadi golle goo gaanin Й—e Й“e woni Й—en e mu'un immorde e keefeeru ko kamЙ“e gollata Й—e."
  23,64,"Haa si Men leptirii neeminaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ka ngurdan aduna Lepte Й—en Г‘alnde Darngal tawa kamЙ“e hiЙ“e towna hitooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko Й“e faabnatooЙ“e."
  23,65,"Wi'anee Й“e ka taЖҙinngol Й“e e Yurmeende Alla nden: ""Wata on haacu wata on Й—aЙ“Й“u faabo e ndee Г‘alaande, ko pellet, on marah walloowo mo no haЙ—ana on immorde e Lepte Alla Й—en""."
  23,66,"GomЙ—ii laatinoke Aayeeje Deftere Alla nden no janngetenoo e dow mooЙ—on ka aduna, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on ruttoo ko on huccuЙ“e(runtii) e gaayi majje, si on nanii Й—e sabu aГұugol Й—e."
  23,67,"HiЙ—on waЙ—a Й—um ko on mawnintiniiЙ“e e dow yimЙ“e Й“en sabu ko aaЖҙiЙ—on kon wonndema onon ko on yimЙ“e hurum on hara le on laataaki yimЙ“e makko; sabu yimЙ“e [hurum on] ko kamЙ“e woni hulooЙ“e Alla Й“en, hiЙ—on hiirira Й“annge [hurum on] ko boni kon immorde e konngol ngol, hara onon on laЙ“Й“inaali mo."
  23,68,"Kaa hara Й“ee sirkooЙ“e taskaaki ko Alla jippini kon ka Alqur'aana fii yo Й“e gomЙ—in nde, Й“e gollira ko woni kon e nder mayre, kaa aru e maЙ“Й“e ko araali maamiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ado maЙ“Й“e? ЖҒe Й—urnii nde Й“e fenni nde."
  23,69,"Kaa hara kamЙ“e Й“e andaali Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) on mo Alla Nuli faade e maЙ“Й“e, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e faytuЙ“e mo? GomЙ—ii Й“e anndiino mo, Й“e anndiino kadi Goongugol makko e hoolaare makko nden."
  23,70,"Ko woni, hiЙ“e wi'a: ""Kanko ko o feetuЙ—o, gomЙ—ii Й“e fenniino, ko woni, o addanii Й“e Goonga kan, kan ka sikke woo alaa e muuЙ—um wonndema ko ka immorde ka Alla, heewuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e ko aГұuЙ“e Goonga kan, ko Й“e aГұuЙ“e ka sabu aГұude mbo e haasidaagu wonngu ka wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e, ej inngan- gol meere maЙ“Й“e nden."
  23,71,"Sinndo Alla naЙ“irno fiyakuuji Й—in, O fewjiri Й—i wano wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in weliraa non kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin bonayno, e Й“en wonuЙ“e e majji sabu majjugol maЙ“Й“e battane fiyakuuji Й—in, ko selli kon e ko boni kon immorde e fewjugol ngol."
  23,72,"Kaa a Й—aЙ“Й“u -an NulaaЙ—o- njoЙ“di immorde e Й“ee e dow ko addanЙ—aa Й“e kon, hara ko Й—um waЙ—i haa Й“e salii noddaandu ndun? ЖҠum iwraali e maaЙ—a, ko mbarjaari Joomi maaЙ—a ndin e njoЙ“di Makko ndin Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude diini mbarjaari Й“ee e tanaa maЙ“Й“e, ko Kanko -SeniiЙ—o On- woni MoЖҙЖҙo Arsikoowo."
  23,73,"Pellet an NulaaЙ—o on, hiЙ—a noddude Й“ee e tanaa maЙ“Й“e faade e laawol focciingol, ngol ooГұannde alah e muuЙ—um, ngol ko Laawol Lislaamu ngol."
  23,74,"E pellet, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—inaali Laakara on e ko woni ton kon immorde e hasboore e Lepte e mbarjaari, ko Й“e ooГұiiЙ“e e Laawol Lislaamu ngol Й“e jokki tanaa maggol immorde e laawi Й“oyliiЙ—i yottinayЙ—i faade e Yiite ngen."
  23,75,"Sinndo Men Yurmino Й“e Men ittani Й“e ko heЙ“i Й“e kon immorde e kokke e heege Й“e duumotono e ndr majjere maЙ“Й“e gaayi Goonga kan hara hiЙ“e mema waЙ—a yaha-yilto."
  23,76,"GomЙ—ii Men jaribiimoЙ“e nooneeji masiibooji, Й“e hoykinanaaki Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й“e yankinanaaki Mo, Й“e yankinaaki Й“e noddi Mo fii yo O ittan Й“e masiibooji Й—in tuma jippagol majji."
  23,77,"Haa nde Men udditunoo e maЙ“Й“e dammbugal immorde e Lepte sattuЙ—e Й—en, e jaka kamЙ“e e nder Й—um ko Й“e taЖҙiiЙ“e e kala welo-welo e moЖҙЖҙere."
  23,78,"Alla O Senike ko Kanko woni On taganЖҠo on -ko onon yo fennuЙ“e immital ngal- nanЙ—e Й—en fii yo on nanirЙ—e, e giiЙ—e Й—en fii yo on yi'irЙ—e, e Й“erЙ—e Й—en fii yo on faamirЙ—e, wonndude e Й—um o yettatah Mo e dow Й—ii neemaaji si wonaa seeЙ—a."
  23,79,"Ko Kanko woni On taguЖҠo on -onon yimЙ“e Й“en- ka leydi, ko faade ka Makko Kanko tun Г‘alnde Darngal mooЙ“oyte Й—on fii hasboore nden e njoЙ“di ndin."
  23,80,"Ko Kanko tun O Senike woni wurnoowo wurnoowo alah tanaa Makko, ko Kanko tun woni waroowo, waroowo alaa tanaa Makko, ko faade ka Makko Kanko tun hoddirtee luutondiral jemma on e Гұalorma on, niwre e ndaygu juutugol e raЙ“Й“iЙ—ugol. Enee on hakkiltaa kattanЙ—e Makko Й—en, e bajjirgol Makko tagugol e fewjugol ngol?!"
  23,81,"Ko woni, Й“e wi'u yeru ko wi'unoo kon baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en e maamiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en ka keefeeru."
  23,82,"ЖҒe wi'i e noone yeddugol woЙ—Й—intina: ""E jaka si men maayii men wontii mbullaari e Жҙi'e kiЙ—Й—e e jaka menen ko men immintinoyteeЙ“e fii hasboore nden hara meЙ—en wuuri?!""."
  23,83,"GomЙ—ii men fodanooma ndee fodoore -Й—um le ko immital Й“aawo mayde nden- maamiraaЙ“e amen Й“en kadi fodano Й—um ko adii, men yi'aali nden fodoore ka waЙ—i, Й—um wonaali si wonaa meere adinooЙ“e Й“en e penaale maЙ“Й“e."
  23,84,"Maakan -an NulaaЙ—o- Й“ee heeferЙ“e yedduЙ“e immital ngal: ""Ko hommbo jeyi ndii leydi, e Й“en wonuЙ“e e hoore mayri si tawii hiЙ—on mari ganndal?"""
  23,85,"Aray Й“e wi'i: ""Leydi ndin e Й“en wonuЙ“e e mayri ko Alla woodani"". Awa maakan Й“e: ""Enee, on annditatah wonndema On jeyЙ—o leydi ndin e Й“en wonuЙ“e e hoore mayri ko O HattanЖҠo e dow wurnitugol on Й“aawo mayde mooЙ—on?"""
  23,86,"MaakanЙ“e: ""Ko hommbo woni Jooma kammuuli Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i? E ko hommbo woni Jooma Arsi mawki kin, kin tawki alaa ko tagaa ko Й“uriki mawnude?"""
  23,87,"Aray Й“e wi'a: ""Kammuuli Й—in jeeЙ—iЙ—i e Arsi mawki kin ko jeyal Alla."" Maakan Й“e: ""Enee, on hulirtah Alla doftagol yamiraaЙ—i Makko Й—in e woЙ—Й—itagol haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in fii yo on hisu immorde e Lepte Makko Й—en?"""
  23,88,"Maakan Й“e: ""Ko e junngo hommbo woni laamu kala huunde, hay e huunde sortotaako e ley Laamu Makko ngun, hara Kanko hiMo faaboo on mo O muuyi immorde e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, alah hay e gooto haЙ—anoowo on mo O muuyani bone, o dunyatah Lepte Й—en e makko, si tawii laatanike on ganndal?"""
  23,89,"Aray Й“e wi'a: ""Laamu kala huunde ko e Junngo Makko woni O Senike. Awa maakan Й“e: ""E ko honno hakkillaaji mo'on Й—in yaari, hiЙ—on rewa tanaa Makko wonndude e qirritagol mooЙ—on Й—um [ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo]""."
  23,90,"Fiyaake on wonaali wano Й“e nodditorta non, ko woni, Men addanii Й“e Goonga ka sikke alah e mu'un, pellelt, kamЙ“e ko fenuЙ“e e ko Й“e nodditii kon wonnde no woodani Alla kafidaaЙ—o e Й“iЙ—Й—o, Alla Toowii gaayi ngol konngol maЙ“Й“e Toowal Mawnungal."
  23,91,"Alla jogitaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o wano heeferЙ“e Й“en aaЖҙori non, reweteeЙ—o e goonga kadi alah wonndude e Makko, sinndo wonno reweteeЙ—o e goonga no wonndi e Makko, reweteeЙ—o kala yaadayno e geЙ“al mu'un ngal immorde e tagu ngu o tagi ngun, yoga maЙ“Й“e foolondirayno e yoga, Й—um bonna njuЙ“Й“udi goodal ngal, ko selli kon, ko wonndema hay e huunde e Й—um waЙ—aali. Ko Й—um tinndini wonndema pellet, ReweteeЙ—o On e Goonga ko Gooto ko Kanko tun woni Alla, O Senike O LaaЙ“ii gaayi e ko sirkooЙ“e Й“en sifotoo Mo kon, kon ko haananah Mo immorde e Й“iЙ—Й—o e kafidaaЙ—o."
  23,92,"AnnduЙ—o kala ko wirnii e tagu Makko ngun, e AnnduЙ—o ko seedetee heftiree so'irЙ—e Й—en, hay e huunde e Й—um suuЙ—anaaki Mo, O Toowii Senayee wonanii Mo nde laatantoo Mo kafidaaЙ—o."
  23,93,"Maaku -Ko an yo NulaaЙ—o-: ""Jooma, si A hollii lam e Й“ee sirkooЙ“e ko foduЙ—aaЙ“e kon immorde e Lepte Й—en""."
  23,94,"Joomam, pellet, battane maЙ“Й“e Й—en min miЙ—o seedii Й—um, wata A waЙ—tidam e maЙ“Й“e sakko heЙ“a lam ko heЙ“i Й“e kon immorde e Lepte Й—en."
  23,95,"Pellet, Menen ko Men HattanЙ“e nde Men waЙ—ay maa hiЙ—a yi'a seedoo ko Men fodiЙ“e kon immorde e Lepte Й—en, Men ronkatah Й—um wanaa kadi e tanaa mu'un [Men ronkata]."
  23,96,"DuГұir -an NulaaЙ—o- on wonЙ—o bonde e maaЙ—a geЙ“al Й“urngal moЖҙЖҙude ngal; Й—um woni yaafaade mo, muГұГұoЙ—aa e dow lorra makko kan, ko Menen Й“uri Anndunde ko Й“e woni kon sifaade immorde e sirku ngun e fennugol ngol, e ko Й“e wonumaa sifaade kon immorde e huunde nde haananaa ma, wano mbilewu e feetere."
  23,97,"Maaku: ""Jooma mi rentorii Ma immorde e hodooje Seytanuuji Й—in e sonwosiyee(sikke sikke) majji""."
  23,98,"Mi moolorii Ma Jooma am nde Й—i tawata lam e nder huunde immorde e fiyakuuji am Й—in."
  23,99,"Haa si mayde nden arii goЙ—Й—o e Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, o yi'i ko woni kon jippaade e makko o wi'i hara ko o nimsuЙ—o e dow ko feЖҙЖҙi kon e ngurdam makko Й—am, e ko o welsindinoo kon e bannge Alla: ""Jooma, ruttam faade ka ngurdam aduna""."
  23,100,"No gasa min, mi gollay ko moЖҙЖҙi si mi ruttike faade e makko [ka aduna]. ЖҠum waЙ—atah, fiyaake on wonaa no Й—aЙ“Й“irЙ—aa non, Й—um ko konngol tun nii, ko kanko wowlingol, hay sinndo o ruttano faade e ngurndam aduna Й—am o humnataano ko o fodi kon, Й“ee maayooЙ“e aray Й“e heddoo e nder heedo hakkonde aduna e Laakara haa Г‘alnde Immital e caakal ngal, Й“e ruttataako immorde e Й—um faade e aduna fii yo Й“e hewtito ko feЖҙЖҙirnoo Й“e kon, Й“e moЖҙЖҙintina ko Й“e bonnunoo kan."
  23,101,"Si Malaa'ikaajo fawaaЙ—o on wuttugol ka alaadu o wuttii wuttannde Й—immere nden noddaynde nden e Darngal ngal, haray dammbe alah hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Й—e Й“e wasorta Й—um, sabu hilnagol maЙ“Й“e kulol Darngal ngal, yoga maЙ“Й“e lanndoytaako yoga sabu hilnagol maЙ“Й“e ngol ko maapini Й“e kon."
  23,102,"Kala mo manndake mu'un teddiri sabu jistugol maЖҙЖҙi makko Й—in e dow bonЙ—i makko Й—in, haray ko Й“en woni malaaЙ“e Й“en sabu heЙ“ugol maЙ“Й“e ko Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“i kon, e ko Й“e woЙ—Й—intee kon immorde e koЙ“e huli kon."
  23,103,"Kala mo manndake mu'un hoyi sabu jistugol bonЙ—i makko Й—in e dow moЖҙЖҙi makko Й—in haray Й“en Й—on ko kamЙ“e woni yeebirЙ“e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in sabu gollugol ko lorrata Й—i kon, e Й—alugol ko nafata Й—i kon immorde e gomЙ—inal e golle moЖҙЖҙe, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e ka Yiite Jahannama, Й“e yaltatah e magge."
  23,104,"Yiite ngen no sunna geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara kamЙ“e e nder magge, toni maЙ“Й“e dowji Й—in e leyji Й—in tagginoke gaayi ГұiiЖҙe maЙ“Й“e Й—en immorde e saЙ—tude ГұirЙ“inagol."
  23,105,"Wi'aneeЙ“e ka duЙ—Й—ugol Й“e: ""Enee, Aayeeje Alqur'aana Й—en laatanooki no janngee e dow mo'on ka aduna, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on fenna Й—e?!"""
  23,106,"ЖҒe wi'i: ""Joomi amen, foolii men ko adii kon ka Ganndal MaaЙ—a immorde e malkiso amen, men woniino yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e gaayi Goonga kan."""
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin men ka Yiite, si men yiltitike faade e ko men wonnoo kon e mu'un immorde e keefeeru e majjere haray menen ko men tooГұuЙ“e wonkiiji amen, gomЙ—ii nganto amen ngon taЖҙii."
  23,108,"Alla Daala: ""HoЙ—ee ka nder Yiite ko on jaasuЙ“e hoynaaЙ“e, wata on haalanam [fii yaltineede]."
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en, Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e Lam, hiЙ“e wi'a: ""Joomi amen, men gomЙ—inii Ma haforan men bakkatuuji amen Й—in, Yurmiraa men Yurmeende MaaЙ—a nden, ko An ЖҒuri MoЖҙЖҙude YurmeteeЙ“e Й“en."
  23,110,"JogitiЙ—on Й“ee gomЙ—inЙ“e noddooЙ“e Joomi mu'un nokku fii jalkitugol hiЙ—o jalnora Й“e, jalnorЙ—on Й“e haa jalnorgol Й“e ngol yejjintini on jaЕӢtagol Alla, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on jala Й“e jalkita."
  23,111,"Min, Mi yoЙ“irii Й“ee gomЙ—inЙ“e heЙ“ugol Aljanna on Г‘alnde Darngal; fii muГұal maЙ“Й“e ngal e dow Й—oftagol Alla e dow ko Й“e laatinoo kon hiЙ“e hawra e mu'un sabu mo'on immorde e lorra."
  23,112,"O Daali: ""No foti heewde ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ—on ka leydi immorde e duuЙ“i? No foti heewde ko yeebuЙ—on ton immorde e waqtu."""
  23,113,"ЖҒe jaabora wi'ugol maЙ“Й“e: ""Men ГұiiЙ“ii Гұallal maaЙ—um seeЙ—a e Гұallal, lanndo Й“en toppitiiЙ“e e limugol ГұalЙ—i e lebbi."""
  23,114,"O Daali: ""On ГұiiЙ“aali ka aduna si wanaa jamaanu hun fanЙ—u kun, no newii muГұГұagol e nder makkun e dow Й—oftaare sinndo onon on laatino hiЙ—on anndi emmbere ГұiiЙ“ugol mooЙ—on."
  23,115,"Kaa on sikku -onon yimЙ“e Й“en- wonndema ko Men Tagiri on ko fijindaaru gaanin ГұeeГұal, hara mbarjaari alah Lepte alah yeru muumi(jawdi) Й—in, hara onon on ruttetaake faade e Amen Г‘alnde Darngal fii Hasboore nden e njoЙ“di ndin?!"
  23,116,"Alla Senike LamЙ—o firlitotooЙ—o e nder tagu Makko ngun ko O muuyi kon, On Mo KaГұum ko O Goonga Konngol Makko ngol ko Goonga, reweteeЙ—o e goonga alah tanaa Makko, Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin, kin ki kaГұum no Й“uri mawnude tageefooji Й—in, on mo laatii Jooma ko Й“uri mawnude kon e tageefooji Й—in haray ko Kanko woni Jooma majji Й—i fow majji."
  23,117,"On mo rewi wonndude e Alla reweteeЙ—o goo hara o maraa hujja jojjiЙ—ugol makko e dewal ngal (ko Й—um woni fiyaake kala rewaaЙ—o tanaa Alla) anndu pellet, njoЙ“di golle makko bonЙ—e Й—en no ka Joomi makko Senaande wonanii Mo, ko Kanko woni On yoЙ“irayЖҠo mo Й—um Leptugol mo, pellet, Kanko O malnirtaa heeferЙ“e Й“en heЙ“ugol ko Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“ata kon, wanah daЙ—ugol ko Й“e hulata kon."
  23,118,"Maaku -an NulaaЙ—o-: ""Joomam haforanam bakkatuuji am Й—in, Yurminiraa mi Yurmeende MaaЙ—a nden ko An woni ЖҒurЙ—o MoЖҙЖҙude kala YurmiiЙ—o jom bakkaatu, jaЙ“u tuubuubuyee am on."""
